abstract="The basis of this study was the ageing of the population all over the world. The study concentrated on finding out the key service needs of elderly people. The service needs from the end users' as well as the experts' perspective were gathered by means of various group methods such ideation sessions. Four mobile communication service concepts were created using these groups' opinions. After diverse communication, these concepts were tested by the elderly. The research methods comprised a user study and a concept study.",
