number="4",
pages="77--97",
abstract="Arguably, the defining technology of the late 20th century was information technology. In this new century, it will continue to increasingly pervade every aspect of our lives from the way we earn our livelihoods to the way we, ourselves, access information, even choose to entertain and inform ourselves, and live our lives. For this reason, it can be particularly informative to look at the key trends in information technology and consider some of the technologies that are and will be disruptive.",
